    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/dbd06fd5125506d71150da0b925c0d21.poster.avif?t=1748724852\" width=636 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/dbd06fd5125506d71150da0b925c0d21.webm?t=1748724852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/dbd06fd5125506d71150da0b925c0d21.mp4?t=1748724852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Step into the pumpkin patch in &quot;Combine 2 Pumpkins&quot;, a physics-based, puzzle-solving adventure where strategy and planning are key to your success - until something inevitably goes wrong. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master the Art of Combination</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/87d40d2f53297904c72371a5e76dcb8c.poster.avif?t=1748724852\" width=640 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/87d40d2f53297904c72371a5e76dcb8c.webm?t=1748724852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/87d40d2f53297904c72371a5e76dcb8c.mp4?t=1748724852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>As the title suggests, the heart of &quot;Combine 2 Pumpkins&quot; lies in its pumpkin-combining mechanic. Customize your pumpkins to match them based on hue, shade, displayed order or all at once! Mix and match  to create powerful reactions!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet Special Pumpkin Personalities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/fa3d2aa81c48a77f5dbef3aad51a78ed.poster.avif?t=1748724852\" width=636 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/fa3d2aa81c48a77f5dbef3aad51a78ed.webm?t=1748724852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/fa3d2aa81c48a77f5dbef3aad51a78ed.mp4?t=1748724852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Discover pumpkins with special abilities that change the way you play. Meet &quot;Burstian&quot; who detonates when paired with others of the same color, &quot;Chromie&quot; who can combine with any other pumpkins, and many more - each with a unique twist, adding depth and strategy to your decisions. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Achieve Explosive Combos</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/27ee2d2236b400409867cacf8d3bee8a.poster.avif?t=1748724852\" width=636 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/27ee2d2236b400409867cacf8d3bee8a.webm?t=1748724852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148100/extras/27ee2d2236b400409867cacf8d3bee8a.mp4?t=1748724852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The more pumpkins you combine, the bigger the payoff! Execute multi-layered combos for massive score boosts! <br>Compete with others on the global leaderboard for the highest score and the Pumpkin Master title!</p>",
